| ---------- | ----------- |
| Left pin   | 5V          |
| Middle pin | A0          |
| Right pin  | GND         |

| LED Leg               | Connects To    |
| --------------------- | -------------- |
| Long leg (anode +)    | D13            |
| Short leg (cathode â€“) | Resistor â†’ GND |

